{
  "stem": "27335.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You see, I'm a-- I'm a Canadian-born.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in those early days, you know, the far Wild West, you know, Canada, all we had to-- I even knew the name.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there really existed a-- a Hungarian teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- I-- and I even met him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Only time, when I was an organizer already in the Saskatchewan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so, it was airtight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- they began to-- to wave it right through the weeks of the interrogation, because I told them the straight story.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were some, especially one, Rose was his name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That little bastard-- he keep-- would never-- he-- he never believed me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- Did you have-- did you have any inmates in the prison, any other people in the same cell?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it-- well it-- not in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the only one, when they-- they put the transfer together, they put me into-- into another cell there with 12 partisans in Soviet uniform, Hungarian boys, who were in Hungarian-- were captured, you know, the prison where they trained them, who volunteered, trained them, partisans around Kiev there, in the training camp there.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they put me among them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By God, I-- [COUGHS] I was-- I was at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[COUGHS] And the-- the-- the head guy was-- was a-- a cabinet maker, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, we spent-- we spent the time together to be shipped to-- to Budapest on the train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Took about-- well, a six-hour train-- train ride from [NON-ENGLISH] to Budapest, about six-hour train ride, maybe less, took them three days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no, no, prisoners' train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A prisoners train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And well, all-- all of the details, [INAUDIBLE] and details in there, all-- are all in my book.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
